## Quick Field Mapping Reference

### SQL Parameter → API Request Property

| SQL Parameter | API Property | Notes |
|---------------|--------------|-------|
| `@SN` | `.Sn` | Serial number (string) |
| `@AOIID` | `.Aoiid` | AOI machine ID (int) |
| `@StationID` | `.StationId` | Station ID (int) |
| `@PartID` | `.PartId` | Part ID (int) |
| `@Side` | `.Side` | "T" or "B" (string, 1 char) |
| `@Trndate` | `.Trndate` | Transaction date (DateTime) |
| `@IsGood` | `.IsGood` | Pass/Fail (boolean) |
| `@IsRework` | `.IsRework` | Is rework (boolean) |
| `@RefCir` | `.RefCir` | Component reference (string) |
| `@DefectDesc` | `.DefectDesc` | Defect description (string) |
| `@UserPass` | `.UserPass` | Manual review result (boolean?) |
| `@Position` | `.Position` | Board position (int) |
| `Facility_Key` | `.FacilityKey` | Facility key (int?) |
| `AreaID` | `.AreaId` | Area ID (int?) |

### Position Coordinates (Optional)

| Field | Property | Type |
|-------|----------|------|
| X Misalignment | `.Xmisfit` | Single? (float) |
| Y Misalignment | `.Ymisfit` | Single? (float) |
| X Position | `.Xpos` | Single? (float) |
| Y Position | `.Ypos` | Single? (float) |

