## Common Patterns to Handle

### Pattern: Empty String to 0 Conversion
```vb
' OLD
If posX = "" Then posX = 0

' NEW (inline)
.Xpos = If(posX = "", 0, CSng(posX))
```

### Pattern: String to Boolean
```vb
' OLD
Dim userResultBit As Boolean = (userResult = "PASS")

' NEW (inline)
.UserPass = (userResult = "PASS")
```

### Pattern: DBNull.Value
```vb
' OLD
New SqlParameter("@UserPass", SqlDbType.Bit) With {.Value = DBNull.Value}

' NEW
.UserPass = Nothing
```

