## Performance Tips

### When to Use Batch vs Single

| Scenario | Recommendation | Reason |
|----------|----------------|--------|
| 1-5 records | Single | Simple, low overhead |
| 10+ records | Batch | 10-100x faster |
| Mixed PASS/FAIL | Batch | Collect all, submit once |
| Real-time updates | Single | Immediate feedback |

### Batch Size Recommendations

| Records | Method | Performance |
|---------|--------|-------------|
| 1-5 | Single | Good |
| 10-100 | Batch | Excellent |
| 100-1000 | Batch | Best |
| 1000+ | Batch with chunking | Best |

### Chunking for Very Large Batches
```vb
' For 1000+ records, split into chunks of 500
Dim chunkSize As Integer = 500
For i As Integer = 0 To aoiInspectionRequests.Count - 1 Step chunkSize
    Dim chunk = aoiInspectionRequests.Skip(i).Take(chunkSize).ToList()
    Dim response = AOI.SubmitInspectionBatch(chunk)
    ' Process response...
Next
```

