## Summary

✅ **Use Template 1** for simple single inserts
✅ **Use Template 2** for inserts with defect information
✅ **Use Template 3** for loop optimization (HUGE performance gain)
✅ **Use Template 4** for complex mixed scenarios

**Remember**:
- Always test after each refactoring
- Use batch operations whenever possible (10-100x faster!)
- Keep existing business logic, only replace SQL operations
